                    "value": "<p>This object, made of silver light, takes the form of a small musical instrument, prop, or other tool associated with a specific art form. The holder of the immaculate instrument never suffers from creative blocks of any kind and their work is always insightful and skilled. A character who uses the immaculate instrument to @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.Item.Perform] or Craft can attempt the check at mythic proficiency once per month, and as long as they possess their immaculate instrument, they treat any critical failures with these skills as failures.</p><hr /><p><strong>Destruction</strong> If the holder uses the immaculate instrument to intentionally produce a work that is not just mediocre or crass, but one that devalues the public opinion of the art form itself in a showing of at least 100 spectators, the instrument fades away in shame.</p>"
